### What problem does this feature solve?
Our vue app uses a fixed height `<div>` as frame container to load all pages inside, like following snippet:
```html
<div style="
     height: 100%; 
     width: 100%;
     position: fixed;
     overflow-x: hidden;
     overflow-y: scroll;
">
     <vue-router />
</div>
```

